3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper discusses the impact of randomization of number of users on the throughput of a system, which is a topic relevant to social and information networks. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper deals with a system with multiple users, which can be considered as a multiagent system.
